## Using compiler-$(environment) for app-foo/bar
# app-foo/bar compiler-clang-hardened compiler-clang-lto clang-chromium

## Clang: Advanced Setup (https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Clang#Advanced_examples)
# compiler-clang-hardened: build with a hardened Clang environment
# compiler-clang-lto: build with Clang-LTO environment
# clang-chromium: build with tweaks specifically for Chromium
dev-lang/spidermonkey compiler-clang-hardened compiler-clang-lto
www-client/firefox compiler-clang-hardened compiler-clang-lto
www-client/librewolf compiler-clang-hardened compiler-clang-lto
www-client/ungoogled-chromium compiler-clang-hardened compiler-clang-lto clang-chromium
